ail investing space with its zero-commission trading platform and user-friendly interface. The company has been able to appeal to an entirely new consumer base as a result of</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1362328147/image_1362328147.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743785-robinhoods-meteoric-rise-redefining-retail-investing", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 12:52:01"}, {"id": "4743782", "title": "Adobe Q4 Earnings: Why This Stock Leaves Me Unsold", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219303803/image_1219303803.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Adobe Headquarters\" data-id=\"1219303803\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4847px\" height=\"3229px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219303803/image_1219303803.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219303803/image_1219303803.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219303803/image_1219303803.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219303803/image_1219303803.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219303803/image_1219303803.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219303803/image_1219303803.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219303803/image_1219303803.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219303803/image_1219303803.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">hapabapa</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>Adobe (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ADBE\" title=\"Adobe Inc.\">ADBE</a></span>) delivered fiscal <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4385705-adobe-non-gaap-eps-of-4_81-beats-0_14-revenue-of-5_61b-beats-70m\">Q4 2024 results</a> that were largely in line with my expectations. Even though I have been neutral on this name for a long while and remain neutral on this stock, I'm somewhat</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219303803/image_1219303803.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743782-adobe-q4-earnings-stock-leaves-me-unsold", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 12:37:08"}, {"id": "4743793", "title": "3 Forces Powering The Nuclear Energy Surge", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1366390149/image_1366390149.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Nuclear power plant with power poles\" data-id=\"1366390149\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1366390149/image_1366390149.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1366390149/image_1366390149.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1366390149/image_1366390149.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1366390149/image_1366390149.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1366390149/image_1366390149.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1366390149/image_1366390149.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1366390149/image_1366390149.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1366390149/image_1366390149.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">querbeet</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>Nuclear energy is emerging as a vital contributor to meeting the surge in global power demand.</em></p> <p>Nuclear energy is back in the spotlight after years in the shadows, subject to debate over its long-term viability and whether its potential benefits (reliable, clean</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1366390149/image_1366390149.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743793-3-forces-powering-nuclear-energy-surge", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 12:30:00"}, {"id": "4743777", "title": "FIGS: Enter A White Knight?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/467393051/image_467393051.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Chess white knight\" data-id=\"467393051\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1017px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/467393051/image_467393051.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/467393051/image_467393051.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/467393051/image_467393051.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/467393051/image_467393051.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/467393051/image_467393051.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/467393051/image_467393051.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/467393051/image_467393051.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/467393051/image_467393051.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">DimaSobko/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Earlier in the year, I wrote a <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4671887-figs-premium-medical-apparel-company-wait-for-reacceleration-in-growth\">cautious</a> article on FIGS, Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/FIGS\" title=\"FIGS, Inc.\">FIGS</a></span>), the purveyor of high-end medical apparel. While the company has gained a cult-like following on social media, I was concerned that it</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/467393051/image_467393051.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743777-figs-enter-a-white-knight", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 12:05:52"}, {"id": "4743779", "title": "I'm Bearish On e.l.f. Beauty For The Coming Years", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1658893205/image_1658893205.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Make up products at pink background top view.\" data-id=\"1658893205\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1658893205/image_1658893205.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1658893205/image_1658893205.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1658893205/image_1658893205.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1658893205/image_1658893205.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1658893205/image_1658893205.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1658893205/image_1658893205.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1658893205/image_1658893205.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1658893205/image_1658893205.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Nadiia Borovenko</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>As many sectors have struggled with of late, high levels of inflation and increased cost of living has notably shifted consumer demand. Some brands have been able to absorb or pass on these costs to consumers, but many targeting</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1658893205/image_1658893205.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743779-bearish-on-elf-beauty-for-coming-years", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 12:00:00"}, {"id": "4743783", "title": "Allspring Adjustable Rate Government Fund Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2178044353/image_2178044353.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Hand holding a debt rate, hand hold increase percent icon, debt increase, interest burden, interest rate rise, Federal Reserve or central bank raising policy, monetary percentage concept\" data-id=\"2178044353\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864p