><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096299665/image_2096299665.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Doctor high fiving young girl in exam room\" data-id=\"2096299665\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096299665/image_2096299665.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096299665/image_2096299665.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096299665/image_2096299665.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096299665/image_2096299665.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096299665/image_2096299665.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096299665/image_2096299665.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096299665/image_2096299665.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096299665/image_2096299665.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">MoMo Productions</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Miller Kampa</em></p> <p><strong>Significant policy proposals could be in store, along with a more business-friendly approach.</strong></p> <p>As President-elect Donald J. Trump prepares for his second term in office, the health care industry is poised for a period of potential change, despite</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096299665/image_2096299665.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743780-navigating-health-care-industry-trump-second-term", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 11:40:00"}, {"id": "4743776", "title": "Aluminum Deficit To Support Prices In 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/180405086/image_180405086.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Stacked ingots in aluminium recycling plant warehouse awaiting delivery\" data-id=\"180405086\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/180405086/image_180405086.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/180405086/image_180405086.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/180405086/image_180405086.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/180405086/image_180405086.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/180405086/image_180405086.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/180405086/image_180405086.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/180405086/image_180405086.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/180405086/image_180405086.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Monty Rakusen</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/ewa-manthey/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ewa Manthey</a></em></p> <h2>Aluminium gets a boost from alumina</h2> <p>Aluminium prices have risen lately, driven by record high alumina prices. Alumina prices jumped to a record this year, squeezing profitability for smelt